The scientists are finding ways to mitigate the pandemic. But what about us? Will we just binge on Netflix? Will we not pray? For healing? For strength? For grace? Will we not turn to God? Or has our society become so liberal and humanistic that we naively think this situation will solve itself someday without any divine intervention? We shouldn't be using this time to take jabs at people who have prejudice against artists. Doctors and local government workers are not getting their recognition, but they keep on.
